{"tid":1921811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己精神好似出現問題但唔敢去睇醫生","createTime":"2020-03-12T07:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T15:08:17.000Z","uid":352882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67d7e4846fa4a38f13e6b3f46cc35a71c53ec811","tid":1921811,"uid":352882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"唔敢去睇<br />\n覺得自己知自己好似病左<br />\n識得咁諗所以唔覺得自己真係病<br />\n但焦慮抑鬱症既病徵中左好多<br />\n成日都想去自殺做野又無晒動力<br />\n到底我應唔應該去醫院睇睇佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28ea96ef696de158dca89a7550a62fbb71442cf","tid":1921811,"uid":265403,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"去睇 始終醫生先係專業<br />\n你有嘅話就食藥醫 無嘅話求個安心都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情緒病、精神病喺香港好平常 唔好覺得自己有問題/好奇怪"},{"pid":"97dd2b58459f0f9615c564f1802acede1a30019e","tid":1921811,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"去睇 真係好想見 咪當傾下計咁"},{"pid":"a54aa73d39ff88eb7aa3608de38c02d3d45a7902","tid":1921811,"uid":215784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"我都想去但好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb50d9bfdf1fe2c7a819287d5d9d1755a4a974d6","tid":1921811,"uid":352882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54aa73d39ff88eb7aa3608de38c02d3d45a7902","tid":1921811,"uid":215784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"我都想去但好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"我都驚好貴<br />\n其實公立醫院有無得就咁去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro